22:50.970 --> 22:54.773 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, that means
that investigation
will definitely be expanded to
include specifically

22:54.807 --> 22:58.143 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
