about?

22:58.177 --> 22:59.378 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

22:59.411 --> 23:01.180 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JAMES RISCH: You know, I don't
know where
it will lead.

23:01.213 --> 23:04.316 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Obviously, we're going to lead
it -- we're
going to take it as far as we
can take it.

23:04.350 --> 23:08.387 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It's important for national
security that
we know.

23:08.420 --> 23:11.991 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Those of us that are in the
first branch of
government that actually fund
these operations

23:12.024 --> 23:17.196 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
