the policy
decisions that we have to make.

23:20.366 --> 23:24.236 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Can you say
whether or not
the investigation is going to
also look in

23:24.270 --> 23:28.907 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
