down?

23:38.017 --> 23:39.451 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

23:39.485 --> 23:41.420 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JAMES RISCH: You know, that's a
fact that
I have seen reported today.

23:41.453 --> 23:45.291 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
