government, and there
are certain areas we don't go
into.

23:58.003 --> 23:59.805 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
This is a person that's very
close to the
president.

23:59.838 --> 24:02.775 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He's not subject to Senate
confirmation.

24:02.808 --> 24:08.347 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And when the president is
getting information,
when he's being advised by these
people, it's

24:08.380 --> 24:14.219 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
important that all those parties
that are
acting in the White House have
an understanding

24:14.253 --> 24:15.554 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
of confidentiality.

24:15.587 --> 24:18.657 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
My point is, I don't know where
this will
go in that regard.

24:18.691 --> 24:22.394 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I know what our sideboards are,
and we will
stay within those sideboards.

24:22.428 --> 24:25.931 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, the White
House press
secretary said today that the
president was

24:25.964 --> 24:27.800 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
