24:35.107 --> 24:36.542 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

24:36.575 --> 24:39.611 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JAMES RISCH: Well, if that fact
has been confirmed,
then it is a fact.

24:39.645 --> 24:44.550 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: But the -- it
sounds like you're
not saying whether or not the
committee is

24:44.583 --> 24:46.685 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
