president's handling
of this.

24:46.719 --> 24:48.520 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

24:48.554 --> 24:52.691 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JAMES RISCH: Well, the
president's handling
of this, I think, is a matter
that is a very

24:52.725 --> 24:55.494 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
