branches of
government.

24:55.527 --> 24:59.331 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I guess what you're asking
is, what was
-- how was he motivated?

24:59.365 --> 25:00.332 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Right.

25:00.366 --> 25:01.467 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

25:01.500 --> 25:03.335 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JAMES RISCH: Why was this done
and what have
you?

25:03.369 --> 25:08.874 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Boy, that's an area that I think
you would
have a very difficult time
getting that information

25:08.907 --> 25:10.075 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
to begin with.

25:10.109 --> 25:12.845 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Certainly, the president
wouldn't be asked
about that.

25:12.878 --> 25:17.015 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And, as a result of that, it
would be very
difficult to dig into that.

25:17.049 --> 25:22.921 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think, if we know the facts,
that's what's
going to help us as we do our
job and move

25:22.955 --> 25:24.690 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
forward.

25:24.723 --> 25:26.425 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, the reason
