in the elections last year.

26:02.261 --> 26:05.531 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Can you tell us anything about
the state of
that investigation?

26:05.564 --> 26:06.532 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

26:06.565 --> 26:07.766 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JAMES RISCH: I can.

26:07.800 --> 26:09.168 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
