things that
we do want to look at.

26:13.539 --> 26:20.412 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We have done the things that you
do as you
prepare and start into an
investigation.

26:20.446 --> 26:25.317 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I have been involved in lots
of these
on the committee, whether it was
Benghazi,

26:25.350 --> 26:29.588 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
whether it was the torture
investigation,
others that we have done that
have not become

26:29.621 --> 26:30.589 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
public.

26:30.622 --> 26:34.393 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And we're good at what we do.

26:34.426 --> 26:41.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We do have excellent cooperation
from the
intelligence community
generally, from the

26:41.066 --> 26:43.135 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
16 intelligence agencies.

26:43.168 --> 26:47.739 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They give us good information
and particularly
when you know exactly what
you're after.

26:47.773 --> 26:51.510 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And so we feel comfortable about
moving forward
with these.

26:51.543 --> 26:56.081 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
