27:08.193 --> 27:09.661 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

27:09.695 --> 27:12.064 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JAMES RISCH: Well, it depends on
the actual
leak that you're talking about.

27:12.097 --> 27:16.168 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
