transcripts.

28:36.848 --> 28:41.787 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Once we see the transcripts,
then, if they
prove as the media has
indicated, they would

28:41.820 --> 28:47.459 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
