the investigation
that we are putting forward by
the Senate

28:47.492 --> 28:54.666 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Intelligence Committee that's
looking at contacts
between former campaign
officials and the

28:54.700 --> 29:00.205 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
