29:08.947 --> 29:14.219 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
This -- General Flynn's actions
would fall
within this investigation.

29:14.252 --> 29:15.887 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And we would need to get to the
bottom of
it.

29:15.921 --> 29:19.257 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
If the facts are as reported,
then I think
the committee needs to interview
him.

29:19.291 --> 29:22.794 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: How do you
determine if the
facts are as reported?

29:22.828 --> 29:23.862 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

29:23.895 --> 29:26.798 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MARK WARNER: Well, we understand
basic tradecraft.

29:26.832 --> 29:33.105 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I would -- this is one of
the things that
just amazes me, that someone
with General

29:33.138 --> 29:38.777 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
