should know that,
if he's talking to a Russian
ambassador, chances

29:38.810 --> 29:41.947 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
are those conversations are
monitored.

29:41.980 --> 29:46.685 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And if they had been monitored,
at some point,
we need to see the transcript.

29:46.718 --> 29:52.958 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Obviously, something has
happened so that
-- because General Flynn relayed
one set of

29:52.991 --> 29:57.229 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
