and then ended
up resigning.

30:01.767 --> 30:08.140 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
If the transcripts reveal what
the press has
said, this raises very, very
serious concerns

30:08.173 --> 30:14.813 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
about potentially an American
who was not
part of an administration at
that point actually

30:14.846 --> 30:20.819 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
trying to undermine then
President Obama's
sanctions against Russia, those
very sanctions

30:20.852 --> 30:24.156 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
which were caused by the Russian
interference
in our electoral process.

30:24.189 --> 30:28.593 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
